title: 大吉
message: Like Amaterasu emerging from the cave, your light shall guide all who see you. Fortune flows freely, and the kami bless your path. Stay humble to preserve this radiance.

title: 大吉
message: As Susanoo triumphed over Orochi, you will overcome trials with courage. Great treasures lie ahead, won by your boldness. The gods smile upon your destiny.

title: 大吉
message: The White Hare of Inaba found healing through kindness. Your compassion will open hidden doors. Prosperity awaits those who act with heart.

title: 中吉
message: Like Urashima Taro in the Dragon Palace, joy comes but may be fleeting. Treasure the present, for time moves swiftly. Your blessings are steady yet delicate.

title: 中吉
message: Benzaiten’s music blesses your tongue and spirit. Success is near if harmony is kept. Speak kindly and rewards shall last.

title: 中吉
message: Raijin’s drums rumble in your fortune, bringing bursts of power. Use them wisely, lest they fade. Balance strength with patience.

title: 小吉
message: The carp climbing the waterfall finds slow but sure triumph. Small blessings pave the way to greater ones. Perseverance is your ally.

title: 小吉
message: Kannon’s mercy shines softly upon you. Your troubles ease little by little. Trust in kindness and steady effort.

title: 小吉
message: Like a hidden gem in the river, fortune reveals itself quietly. Notice the small signs. From them, larger blessings will grow.

title: 吉
message: Hachiman guards your journey with quiet strength. Progress comes with discipline and faith. Do not hurry, for fortune grows slowly.

title: 吉
message: As Inari’s fox spirits protect the fields, your work will yield blessings. Patience and diligence are required. Trust the harvest to come.

title: 吉
message: Ebisu’s laughter blesses you with steady fortune. What you seek will arrive, though later than expected. Remain cheerful and steadfast.

title: 半吉
message: A farmer who sows carefully reaps half the harvest. Your efforts will be rewarded, though modestly. Endurance is the bridge to fullness.

title: 半吉
message: Like a ship guided by half a sail, your path moves slowly yet surely. Do not despair, for progress exists. The gods grant you part of your wish.

title: 半吉
message: As half the moon lights the night, so too does fortune partially favor you. Wait for the full light. Your patience will be tested.

title: 末吉
message: A traveler guided by the North Star walks toward future blessings. Though far away, fortune awaits. Do not stray from your road.

title: 末吉
message: Like a cherry blossom yet to bloom, your happiness is promised but not present. Time alone reveals its beauty. Persevere with faith.

title: 末吉
message: Okuninushi’s trials brought him later glory. Your hardships now are seeds of tomorrow’s prosperity. Endure, for joy is near.

title: 凶
message: Like Izanami lost in Yomi, shadows may cling to you. Be cautious in your steps. Only endurance leads back to light.

title: 凶
message: Storms of Susanoo may test your strength. Chaos surrounds you, but patience deflects harm. Guard against reckless choices.

title: 凶
message: Like bamboo in winter, fortune feels brittle. Yet resilience will save you. Avoid haste, and misfortune will lessen.

title: 大凶
message: The great serpent devours all in its path. Beware sudden loss and calamity. Only humility and prayer may soften the blow.

title: 大凶
message: As the capital once burned in great fires, so too may ruin threaten. Prepare your heart for hardship. Renewal comes only after ashes.

title: 大凶
message: When the sun goddess hid in the cave, the world fell to darkness. Fortune is veiled from you. Seek wisdom in suffering.
